{"tid":1167491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實任正非幾醒","createTime":"2019-05-23T05:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T05:33:01.000Z","uid":113633,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f29a5d4f95abb4d7fb9fa65d897413986738438f","tid":1167491,"uid":113633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:17:52.000Z","msg":"最近好多人笑尻google唔同華為合作，睇下中國點死。連登仔其實同大陸人一樣，好撚鐘意張咩事都拉到民族維度。你笑話人地個女都用iphone，唔用自己品牌。有冇諗過其實係特登，<br />\n&quot;任正非在接受中國媒體群訪時表示，自己的小孩也用蘋果，這不代表不愛華為，&ldquo;不能說用華為產品就愛國，不用就是不愛國。華為產品只是商品，如果喜歡就用，不喜歡就不用，不要和政治掛鉤&hellip;&hellip;千萬不能煽起民粹主義的風。&quot;"},{"pid":"fb1d433a727cd1e4794f2bd43204e730ea96d83a","tid":1167491,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"醒係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db562587085e461ca9d9cf40b56c41a10f457cc","tid":1167491,"uid":113633,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fb1d433a727cd1e4794f2bd43204e730ea96d83a","tid":1167491,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"醒係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"唔會張商品同政治扯上關係"},{"pid":"19fa19802d8a4c623d40c5df8510055c29c773b0","tid":1167491,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb1d433a727cd1e4794f2bd43204e730ea96d83a","tid":1167491,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"醒係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"唔想比人擺上台囉 <br />\n佢求財咋嘛<br />\n<br />\n不過唔到佢揀"}]}